Package services.subservices

package services.subservices
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AccountService
    Service class responsible for account-related functionality such as: - Changing passwords for all user types (Applicant, Officer, Manager) - Registering new applicants into the system This class interacts with user databases and performs input validation during account modification or creation workflows.
    AuthService
    Service class responsible for authentication and login-related logic.
    EnquiryService
    Service class that handles all enquiry-related operations such as adding, viewing, editing, replying to, and deleting enquiries.
    OfficerApplicationService
    Service class that handles officer application processes, including submission, filtering, retrieval, and status updates.
    ProjectApplicationService
    Service class that handles all functionalities related to project applications submitted by applicants, including application submission, status updates, withdrawals, bookings, and eligibility checks.
    ProjectManagementService
    Service class for managing BTO projects.
    ReceiptPrintService
    Service class responsible for generating booking receipts for applicants who have successfully secured a BTO flat.
    ReportPrintService
    Service class responsible for generating detailed reports on booked project applications.
